    <domain>software-developer</domain>
    <summary>Circuit breaker pattern for microservice resilience: three-state machine (CLOSED/OPEN/HALF_OPEN) that stops cascading failures by short-circuiting calls to unhealthy dependencies.</summary>
    <tags>
      <tag>microservices</tag>
      <tag>circuit-breaker</tag>
      <tag>resilience</tag>
      <tag>fault-tolerance</tag>
      <tag>distributed-systems</tag>
    </tags>
